# Python Project Standards

<rule>
name: python_package_management
description: Standards for Python package management using uv
filters:
  - type: file
    pattern: "pyproject.toml"

actions:
  - type: suggest
    message: |
      When managing Python packages with uv:
      - Use `uv add --dev {package}` for development dependencies
      - Do not manually edit pyproject.toml for dependencies
      - Do not use Poetry-specific configurations
</rule>
